abstract: >-
  Open-source reference architecture connecting industrial
  edge sensor hardware (STEVAL-STWINBX1 / STWIN.box) to
  LLM-based diagnostic assistants (Claude) via the Model
  Context Protocol (MCP). Includes MCP servers for sensor
  acquisition and vibration signal processing (FFT, envelope
  analysis, bearing fault detection, ISO 10816), plus Claude
  Skills for guided condition monitoring, fault diagnosis,
  and operator-friendly report generation.
